-- tf.h3: How to create custom component, using default attributes?

`FTD` lang is flexible and you can define your custom names to the default component.
Below are few examples of custom names:

-- cb.code: `-- emoji-list` with custom name as e.g. `showcase`:
lang: ftd

\-- emoji-list.emoji-list showcase: 
string emoji:
caption or body body:
emoji: $emoji
body: $body

\-- emoji-list.emoji-list showcase: $body
string emoji:
caption or body body:
emoji: $emoji





